sn.def:
A liquid terpene, obtained from the crane's-bill (
               Geranium maculatum
            ), and having a peculiar mulberry odor.

entry.def:
A glucoside found in licorice root (
            Glycyrrhiza
         ), in monesia bark (
            Chrysophyllum
         ), in the root of the walnut, etc., and extracted as a yellow, amorphous powder, of a bittersweet taste.

entry.q:
Follow thy drum;
With man's blood paint the ground; gules
         gules.
